{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c6b51fda50","title":"关于《水浒》的评论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bf1e6ab75f","index":0,"year":1975,"month":8,"day":14,"articleId":"c6b51fda50"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoxuan-jinghuo","name":"毛泽东选集1-7（静火版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"静火","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/maoxuan-jinghuo.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoxuan-jinghuo":{"comments":[{"id":"582bc02005","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"这是毛泽东同志关于学习《水浒》〔1〕的谈话。"},{"id":"bc435b1cea","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《水浒》，即《水浒传》，又称《忠义水浒传》，明初小说家施耐庵根据《大宋宣和遗事》及有关话本与民间流传的水浒故事加工整理而成。主要版本有明嘉靖年间武定侯郭勋刻本《忠义水浒传》，一百回本；明杨定见刻本《忠义水浒全传》，一百二十回本；清金圣叹评点本《第五才子书水浒传》，七十一回本。\n这三种版本，人民文学出版社后来都出过重排本。"},{"id":"847f9d3cea","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":17,"text":"晁盖，《水浒传》中梁山早期领袖。"},{"id":"ad0979ff61","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":28,"text":"宋江，《水浒传》中为第一号人物，为梁山起义军领袖，力主接受招安，并最终导致了起义军和他自己的悲剧命运。"},{"id":"189f5dad42","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":4,"part_index":2,"offset":64,"text":"高俅，《水浒传》中朝廷方代表，反面角色，贪官污吏。"},{"id":"bd98d0e8f2","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":5,"part_index":2,"offset":98,"text":"方腊，《水浒传》中另一支农民起义军。"},{"id":"3eec08d56f","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","index":6,"part_index":3,"offset":34,"text":"李逵、吴用、阮小二、阮小五、阮小七，《水浒传》中的英雄好汉，反对招安。"}],"contents":[{"id":"58d79598c0","type":"title","text":"关于《水浒》的评论","index":0,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"bc435b1cea","type":"paragraph","text":"《水浒》这部书，好就好在投降。做反面教材，使人民都知道投降派。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"847f9d3cea","type":"paragraph","text":"《水浒》只反贪官，不反皇帝。屏晁盖于一百零八人之外。宋江投降，搞修正主义，把晁的“聚义厅”改为“忠义堂”，让人招安了。宋江同高俅的斗争，是地主阶级内部这一派反对那一派的斗争。宋江投降了，就去打方腊。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"ad0979ff61","type":"paragraph","text":"这支农民起义队伍的领袖不好，投降。李逵、吴用、阮小二、阮小五、阮小七是好的，不愿意投降。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"189f5dad42","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅评《水浒》评得好，他说：“一部《水浒》，说得很分明：因为不反对天子，所以大军一到，便受招安，替国家打别的强盗——不‘替天行道’的强盗去了。终于是奴才。”（《三闲集·流氓的变迁》）","index":4,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"bd98d0e8f2","type":"paragraph","text":"金圣叹把《水浒》砍掉了二十多回。砍掉了，不真实。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"3eec08d56f","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅非常不满意金圣叹，专写了一篇评论金圣叹的文章《谈金圣叹》（见《南腔北调集》）。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"},{"id":"33dd931b7c","type":"paragraph","text":"《水浒》百回本、百二十回本和七十一回本，三种都要出。把鲁迅的那段评语印在前面。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50"}],"page":{"id":"4ccd069aee","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"c6b51fda50","start":1768,"end":1768}}}},"__N_SSG":true}